---

<section class="manifesto">
  <div class="glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap manifesto-inner" data-reveal>
    <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center">Our one rule</span>
    <h2>AI <span class="accent">and</span>,<br />not AI instead.</h2>
    <p>
      I use AI every day, and I'm upfront about that. It lets me move faster and take on more than one
      person usually could. What it doesn't do is make the calls. I make every real decision, and I go
      over the details AI is happy to skim past, because that is the part you end up feeling even if you
      can't point to it.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-block: clamp(78px, 11vw, 140px);
  }
  .manifesto .glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: min(90vw, 760px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.72 0.06 272 / 0.18), transparent 66%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .manifesto-inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .manifesto h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 5.2rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 14px 0 0;
  }
  .manifesto p {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.7vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 54ch;
    margin: 22px auto 0;
  }
</style>
